  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Lucerne</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532}" title="Montana Art Deco Hotel">Montana Art Deco Hotel</a></h3>
<h3><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106111/hotel_montana_lucerne_beach_club.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/744f079863344c0e9d26748df4c9fc1b" /></h3>
<p>Enjoy incredible views over the city and Lake Lucerne from the Hotel Montana's peaceful hillside location. Grab a drink on the Beach Club Terrace, or eat in the award-winning restaurant. With comfortable rooms and great service, this hotel is a fantastic base from which to explore Lucerne. The private elevator gives easy access to the waterfront.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b87c59db056b49bab449f30036cd51c7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b87c59db056b49bab449f30036cd51c7}" title="Hotel Waldstätterhof">Hotel Waldstätterhof</a></h3>
<h3><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106112/hotel_waldstatterhof_lucerne_typical_premium_double_room.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/d429add1b0fd4e3eb4a741dcce6c3def" /></h3>
<p>Located in central Lucerne, only a few minutes from the train station, exploring the city from the Waldstätterhof couldn't be easier. Rooms are modern and comfortable and the kitchen produces a good range of vegetarian and gluten-free options making it a great choice if you have specific dietary requirements.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Lucerne</a></p>
<h2>Hotel in St. Moritz</h2>
<h3>Hotel Monopol</h3>
<p>This welcoming hotel has a relaxed atmosphere and fabulous views over the town, with a convenient central location close to the amenities and just a short walk from the Corviglia funicular.  A little oasis of luxury with 73 spacious rooms, a rooftop spa and outstanding service. Restaurant Mono offers Italian-Mediterranean cuisine.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Zermatt</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068}" title="Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa">Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104685/le-mirabeau-garten-_-haupthaus.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ed440d94eb384a25ae913d75e3711b96" /></p>
<p>This chic and elegant hotel is the perfect spot for a mountain holiday in style and is popular with guests who return year after year. Soak your muscles in the Alpine Hideaway Spa, relax in the garden or treat yourself to a cocktail in Marie's Deli.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f}" title="Hotel Alex">Hotel Alex</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104686/wellness_whirlpool-030-lowres.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/94a8255dc66943a48a2ab979b1550ef6" /></p>
<p>This elegant hotel has impressive, grand décor and excellent wellness facilities. With a convenient location, close to the train station and Gornergrat mountain railway, plus impeccable service, it's a fantastic place to base yourself to relaxing and exploring Zermatt.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View All Hotels in Zermatt</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
